    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Empowering Women in the Music Industry | Artist showcase - Day 2 |  Fri, May 1, 2026, 7:00 pm | Fourth Stage"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/40726/samantha_christ_francois__credit_to_lilien_trujillo_viton-02__large.png"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "This event is part of the Empowering Women in the Music Industry Conference presented by Axé WorldFest in partnership with the National Arts Centre.\n\nShowcase schedule:\n\nDoors open – 6:30 PM\n\nSamantha Christ Quartet – 7:00 PM\n\nSiibii – 7:45 PM\n\nKazdoura – 8:20 PM\n\nMireya Ramos – 9:40 PM\n\nAbout the conference:\n\nEWIMI6 is a three-day, multi-venue conference and showcase program featuring 17 events across 9 venues, including live and DJ showcases, networking, pitching, keynotes, panels, workshops, mentorship, and wellness activities. \n\nThe 2026 theme, Cultural Connectors, highlights artists and cultural workers as bridges between communities and cultures,..."
      }
    ],
