      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Calling all jazz & musical theatre lovers. Come celebrate the launch of Genna G and her jazz trio’s debut studio album, performed live for the first time ahead of its official release. Hot off the heels of a *nearly* Sold-Out Holiday cabaret, Genna Giampaolo shares a sneak peek of this vulnerable collection of her original songs (as well as a few favourite covers) brought to life by talented collaborators: Nic Code, Mike Mopas and Quinn Beneteau. CDs will be available..."
      }
    ],
