      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Three things to know: This joyful, high-octane tribute to Aretha Franklin includes all your favourite songs from the Queen of Soul and the artists who inspired her.  A star of stage and screen, Capathia Jenkins..."
      }
