    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#title": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Manifesto | Stephanie Lake Company | Apr 9 - 10, 2026 | Babs Asper Theatre"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#image": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "https://naccnaca-eventimages.s3.amazonaws.com/38369/_0000_untitledpref_2_manifesto_roy_vandervegt__large.jpg"
      }
    ],
    "http://ogp.me/ns#description": [
      {
        "@language": "en-ca",
        "@value": "Nine dancers. Nine drummers.\n\nDistinguished Australian choreographer Stephanie Lake’s latest work is an explosive ode to optimism that drives the audience to its feet. Inspired by the opulence of Old Hollywood and the stirring the stirring, primal quality of rhythm, Manifesto’s percussive power is infectious. Dancers and drummers from a range of backgrounds—from contemporary and ballet to salsa and hip hop, from jazz and metal to classical and experimental—vie to see who can unleash more joy on stage. \n\nKnown for her ingenuity at creating..."
      }
    ],
