    "http://schema.org/description": [
      {
        "@language": "en",
        "@value": "Procession explores the ritual of moving together in formation and celebrates the power of performance. Featuring a newly arranged Baroque-inspired score infused with a modern touch, Procession is a bold and captivating commission that reflects the company&rsquo;s spirit of creativity.&nbsp;"
